The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Metro | Good Morning
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       Good Morning
      Hello It's Monday , July 21 , 2008                    
	Roads to avoid     Trinamul Rally through CR Avenue, JL Nehru Road, SN Banerjee Road, Lenin Sarani, Chowringhee, Brabourne Road, Strand Road, Bentinck Street, GC Avenue, College Street and Hazra crossing to observe Martyrs Day, 10am.    
	Tee off    Unveiling of The Telegraph Cup Golf presented by Tata Steel in association with Ballantines at Maidan Bowling Tent, 12.30pm.    
	Launch    Launch of Hyderabad Hazir Hai: Writings from the City of Nizams by author Vanaja Banagiri at Crossword Bookstore, Elgin Road, 6pm.     
	Interaction    Interaction with Pt Shiv Kumar Sharma and filmmaker Jabbar Patel followed by the screening of Antardhwani at Starmark, South City Mall, 3pm.     
	Art watch    La terre, an exhibition at Gallery Nakshatra, noon to 7.30pm.     Abani Sens Whispered Legacy at Emami Chisel Art, Emami Tower, 11am to 7pm.                                                                                                                                                                 
